channel.description: I was talking to defyboy the other day and he was telling me a few tricks at understanding how the new engine packets work. one of them he said was to basically dump whats going on in the stream class by modifying a deob and walking around and performing actions. pretty cool idea im gonna try it later and ill post some of the outputs.
